---
/**
 * Slide 04 · debt-free-affordability — single huge number, $75/month.
 * Source: src/content/messages/debt-free-affordability.md
 */
const id = 'affordability';
---

<section data-slot="04" data-variant="baseline" id={id} class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800 vibrant:bg-slate-950 snap-start">
  <span class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-xs tracking-widest text-gray-400 dark:text-slate-500 vibrant:text-orange-500/80 font-mono">04 / 09</span>

  <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-orange-400 mb-8">Affordability</p>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:gap-12 mb-16">
    <div class="flex items-baseline">
      <span class="text-7xl md:text-9xl lg:text-[10rem] font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-50 vibrant:text-stone-50 leading-none">$75</span>
      <span class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-stone-300 ml-3">/ month</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-200 max-w-md md:mb-6 mt-6 md:mt-0 leading-snug">
      The capped out-of-pocket cost for a B.A. at Reach, after financial aid.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl border-t border-gray-300 dark:border-slate-600 vibrant:border-orange-500/40 pt-10">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-orange-400 mb-2">Two B.A. programs</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-200 leading-relaxed">B.A. in Liberal Studies and B.A. in Global Education both cap at $75/month.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-orange-400 mb-2">Why this works</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-200 leading-relaxed">Affordability is structural, not promotional — the model only works because employers and the workplace carry the practicum.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-orange-400 mb-2">Graduate caveat</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-200 leading-relaxed">Graduate programs route affordability through employer and county-grant pathways, not Reach scholarships.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-12 text-lg italic text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-200 max-w-3xl">
    "Nobody should be forced to choose between a job and a degree."
  </p>
</section>
